### Find most popular artist

msg.data: Find most popular artist

paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT ds.*
FROM (SELECT es_user.user_id, es_song.artist_name, count(es_song.artist_name) as c,
            ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY es_user.user_id ORDER BY COUNT(es_song.artist_name) DESC) as seqnum
     FROM es_song,es_user
     GROUP BY es_user.user_id, es_song.artist_name
    ) ds
WHERE seqnum = 1
ORDER BY c, user_id DESC ;
%pyspark

msg.data: Find top 10 frequent paid users

paragraphs.text:

SELECT userid, count(*) as c
FROM events
WHERE level != 'free' and userid!=""
GROUP BY userid
ORDER BY c DESC
LIMIT 10

### Find favorite artist by gender

msg.data: Find favorite artist by gender

paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT ds.*
FROM (SELECT es_user.gender, es_song.artist_name, count(es_song.artist_name) as c,
            ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY es_user.gender ORDER BY COUNT(es_song.artist_name) DESC) as seqnum
     FROM es_song,es_user
     GROUP BY es_user.gender, es_song.artist_name
    ) ds
WHERE seqnum = 1
ORDER BY c, gender DESC ;
